info.name: ATTOM API
info.description:
## Authentication

ATTOM API uses API Key authentication. On the **Authorization** tab, select Type as **API Key** and add your API key as a header named `apikey`.

## Response Format

The default response format (`Accept` header) has been set to JSON (`application/json`). You may switch to `application/xml` in the **Pre-request Script** tab, if you prefer an XML response.

## Query Parameters

The **Variables** tab has been populated with most common values for query parameters. Except for the variables named in all CAPS (e.g., PROP_API_PREFIX), these values may be overriden to match your needs.
